The paper deals with the problem of quantizing sparse signals, which is a fundamental problem in information theory (cs.IT) and signal processing (cs.SP). The proposed method is inspired by group testing theory, which is a topic in both information theory and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the computational burden of the proposed method, which is a topic in multimedia (cs.MM) and systems and control (cs.SI).
